					<common:category level="1">Metals and semimetals</common:category>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Neodymium(III) oxide or neodymium sesquioxide is a chemical compound composed of neodymium and oxygen. It forms very light grayish-blue hexagonal crystals. The rare-earth mixture didymium, partially consists of neodymium(III) oxide. It oxidizes readily in air to form an oxide, Nd2O3, which easily spalls, exposing the metal to further oxidation. It is a highly insoluble thermally stable neodymium source suitable for glass, optic and ceramic applications.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氧化钕（III）或二氧化钕是一种由钕和氧组成的化合物。它形成非常浅的灰蓝色六角形晶体。稀土混合物镨的部分成分是氧化钕（III）。它在空气中容易氧化，形成氧化物 Nd2O3，这种氧化物很容易剥落，使金属进一步氧化。它是一种高度不溶解的热稳定钕源，适合玻璃、光学和陶瓷应用。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>Nd2O3</sumFormula>
